    <h1>Retail Media Network</h1>
    <p class="description">An advertising ecosystem operated by a retailer that sells brands ad placements across its owned digital and physical properties, using <strong>first-party purchase data</strong> to target shoppers at the moment they are ready to buy.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
