            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Programmatic advertising buys inventory across open-web exchanges using third-party or second-party data. Retail media is sold by the retailer directly and uses that retailer's first-party purchase data. Retail media is typically lower-funnel and more measurable; programmatic is broader reach.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

